 copyright and published with notice) that may be copyrighted.  Responsibility for making an independent legal assessment of an item and securing any necessary permissions ultimately rests with persons desiring to use the item.</p>\n<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.017402, "shard": "02", "shelf_id": "2017218598, 1914-02-21, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/ak", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["united states", "alaska", "seward (alaska)", "seward", "newspapers"], "subject_headings": ["Seward (Alaska)--Newspapers", "Alaska--Seward", "United States--Alaska--Seward"], "subjects": [{"alaska": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:alaska&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"seward": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:seward&fo=json"}, {"seward (alaska)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:seward+%28alaska%29&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2024-05-22T20:40:28.966Z", "title": "Seward daily gateway (Seward, Alaska), February 21, 1914", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2017218598/1914-02-21/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2017218598/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/2017218598", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/de92a830-0f95-5228-8050-5d3f96963b7e"], "batch": ["ak_harborseal_ver04"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1905", "description": ["Daily (except Sunday) Began with vol. I, no. 94 (November 23, 1905); ceased with vol. 8, number 241 (July 21, 1914). Also available on microfilm from the Alaska Historical Society. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Description based on: Vol. I, No. 94 (November 23, 1905); title from masthead. Latest issue consulted: Vol. 8, No. 241 (July 21, 1914). Seward gateway (Seward, Alaska : 1914) 2692-6725 (DLC)sn2008058232 (OCoLC)275163299"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:11.512Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-11", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-11"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2017218598/", "image_url": [], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [60.1000798, -149.4421227], "location": ["alaska", "united states", "seward"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-149.4421227, 60.1000798], "number": ["sn98059811", "http://www.loc.gov/item/2017218598/1914-07-21/ed-1/", "986789018", "1", "2024-05-12t17:51:13.897021", "2692-6679", "331", "online resource", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2025-07-01t13:41:10.600000", "2017218597", "2017218598", "sn2008058232", "http://www.loc.gov/item/2017218598/1905-11-23/ed-1/"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["chronicling america", "catalog", "serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "seward daily gateway (seward, alaska) 1905-1914"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 44.367302, "shelf_id": "Newspaper", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["united states", "alaska", "seward (alaska)", "seward", "newspapers"], "timestamp": "2026-07-22T07:25:07.928Z", "title": "Seward daily gateway", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/